Class BinarySearchTree<TKey extends Comparable<TKey>,Value>

java.lang.Object
BinarySearchTree<TKey,Value>
Type Parameters:
TKey - the type of keys maintained by this tree, must be comparable
Value - the type of mapped values
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBinarySearchTree<TKey,Value>
public class BinarySearchTree<TKey extends Comparable<TKey>,Value> extends Object implements IBinarySearchTree<TKey,Value>
Implements a binary search tree (BST) data structure. This implementation includes self-balancing capabilities (AVL-like rotations) upon insertion.
